  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/61ad4eb463db2abddc7730d7ad264fff.avif?t=1731677827\" width=630 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MIDNIGHT GETAWAY is a top-down getaway driving game set in the decrepit hellhole called Midnight City. You play as the getaway driver of a small crew of misfit criminals with huge ambitions, dead set on making it out of the city after amassing a personal fortune robbing banks. Are you skilled enough to outrun the cops? Or will you crash and burn as many other like-minded criminals have before you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/da8392f5a0806f149802e35b8098dcd5.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/da8392f5a0806f149802e35b8098dcd5.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=428 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Escape the police by doing crazy manoeuvres<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blow up chasing cops while driving 200mph in a city block<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Press SHIFT to bring up your Gear shift<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shift gears quickly to make quick turns and to max out your speed<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > press Q and E to dodge bullets while racing through the city<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/a9083639052a234a0bea83c3c68aa460.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/a9083639052a234a0bea83c3c68aa460.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet your colorful crew of fellow criminals<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Drive your crewmates to safety after they rob Midnight City's banks<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Watch as your gang shoot cops behind you, while you focus on driving!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/steam_image.png\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play through 6 Levels where you discover the streets of Midnight City<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to go as fast as possible! Keep track of your time with the in-game timer<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Quickly restart a level with 'R'<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/9829d1b24b502604207cdcb5a6e8e034.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/9829d1b24b502604207cdcb5a6e8e034.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Will you be the one who makes it out of the city?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You better learn how to drive stick, buddy.</h2></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/61ad4eb463db2abddc7730d7ad264fff.avif?t=1731677827\" width=630 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MIDNIGHT GETAWAY is a top-down getaway driving game set in the decrepit hellhole called Midnight City. You play as the getaway driver of a small crew of misfit criminals with huge ambitions, dead set on making it out of the city after amassing a personal fortune robbing banks. Are you skilled enough to outrun the cops? Or will you crash and burn as many other like-minded criminals have before you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/da8392f5a0806f149802e35b8098dcd5.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/da8392f5a0806f149802e35b8098dcd5.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=428 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Escape the police by doing crazy manoeuvres<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blow up chasing cops while driving 200mph in a city block<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Press SHIFT to bring up your Gear shift<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shift gears quickly to make quick turns and to max out your speed<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > press Q and E to dodge bullets while racing through the city<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/a9083639052a234a0bea83c3c68aa460.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/a9083639052a234a0bea83c3c68aa460.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet your colorful crew of fellow criminals<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Drive your crewmates to safety after they rob Midnight City's banks<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Watch as your gang shoot cops behind you, while you focus on driving!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/steam_image.png\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play through 6 Levels where you discover the streets of Midnight City<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to go as fast as possible! Keep track of your time with the in-game timer<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Quickly restart a level with 'R'<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras/9829d1b24b502604207cdcb5a6e8e034.avif?t=1731677827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244240/extras_big/9829d1b24b502604207cdcb5a6e8e034.avif?t=1731677827 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Will you be the one who makes it out of the city?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You better learn how to drive stick, buddy.</h2></p></li></ul>",
